@HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### =========================================================
### System Endpoints
### =========================================================

### Get Database Status
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/system/database-status
Accept: application/json

###

### Get System Status
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/system/status
Accept: application/json

###

### Get System Health
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/system/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Get System Version
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/system/version
Accept: application/json

###

### Get System Info
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/system/info
Accept: application/json

###

### Get System Time
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/system/time
Accept: application/json

###


### =========================================================
### Enterprise Authentication & Recovery Endpoints
### =========================================================

### 1. Register a new user
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json
User-Agent: VSCode HTTP Client

{
  "email": "testuser@cverify.ai",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "confirmPassword": "Password123!",
  "fullName": "Test User"
}

###

### 2. Verify Email Address (Use token from outbox/email)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/auth/verify-email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_TOKEN_HERE"
}

###

### 3. Resend Verification Link (Enforces 1-minute cooldown)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/auth/resend-verification
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@cverify.ai"
}

###

### 4. Login (Successful only after email is verified)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@cverify.ai",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

###

### 5. Forgot Password / Request Recovery (Enforces cooldown & enumeration prevention)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@cverify.ai"
}

###

### 6. Reset Password
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_TOKEN_HERE",
  "password": "NewPassword456!",
  "confirmPassword": "NewPassword456!"
}

###

### 7. Get Current User Profile (Requires Login HTTP Cookie)
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Accept: application/json

###

### 8. Refresh Token (Rotates session tokens)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh-token
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 9. Logout (Globally invalidates active session)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json
